metadata.name: İntake of Breath 1
metadata.description:
Sometimes life is all about waiting and hoping, because all you can do is waiting and hoping the best. İt was a day like that for her. And I had to distract her, so I did my best and take some photos of her. Still you can see the worry and blues in her eyes.

Created by: Adem Eroğlu Edition: 1/1
